{"word":"πεινάω","slug":"πεινάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>πεινάω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el>πένομαι</el> ‘be poor/needy’] <b>be hungry, hunger<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> in physical sense <b><a href='B:470 4:2'>Mt 4:2</a>; <a href='B:470 25:35'>25:35</a>; <a href='B:480 11:12'>Mk 11:12</a>; <a href='B:490 6:3'>Lk 6:3</a>; <a href='B:520 12:20'>Ro 12:20</a>; <a href='B:530 4:11'>1 Cor 4:11</a>; <a href='B:530 11:21'>11:21</a>; <a href='B:570 4:12'>Phil 4:12</a>; <a href='B:730 7:16'>Rv 7:16</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ metaph.\">metaph.</a> of strong desire for <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> <b><a href='B:470 5:6'>Mt 5:6</a>; <a href='B:490 6:21'>Lk 6:21</a>, <a href='B:490 6:25'>25</a>; <a href='B:500 6:35'>J 6:35</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prob.\">prob.</a> in the combined sense of a and b <b><a href='B:490 1:53'>Lk 1:53</a></b> (anticipating <a href='B:490 9:12-17'>9:12-17</a> with grant of food, and the end-time perspective in 6:21, 25)<b>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:πεῖν\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:πεῖρα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}